      "content": "I get what you're saying about systemic factors, but for the literature review I need to be specific about the actual numbers. When you look at the raw statistics—like FBI Uniform Crime Reporting data or similar datasets—what do the actual correlations between specific racial categories and crime types (like violent vs property crime) look like? I'm trying to map out the data points that researchers often debate.",
